"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anandamayi108\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1824bbcbf14ea7e674c8f3c1bf788538?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1824bbcbf14ea7e674c8f3c1bf788538?s=32&amp;d=monsterid&amp;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anandamayi108\" class=\"reviewer-name\">anandamayi108</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 2, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I would like to say thank you to Modern Tribe. After using the free Events Calendar plugin, very happily for about 2 years, we decided to upgrade to the Events Calendar Pro. In the process, we found out that Modern Tribe offers it to approved charities, for free. As a charity, we were so happy to find this out, and applied. And they granted our request.\nThis is amazing, that a plugin is so philanthropic, offering such valuable support to charities. Therefore, I would like to highly recommend the Events Calendar, not only as a fabulous looking plugin, with great functionality and design, but also a great plugin company to support, while they support others. Thank you.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent plugin to use with Avada</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vikram_mann\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8f610aa3d8e60defa480d57eea8a28e3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8f610aa3d8e60defa480d57eea8a28e3?s=32&amp;d=monsterid&amp;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vikram_mann\" class=\"reviewer-name\">vikram_mann</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 31, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I am front end developer and have used this plugin in 100s websites. Excellent work guys and keep it up. Thanks</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good Plugin ,</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/janweisser\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/45ee51ed7654e7d031143173c15abe93?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/45ee51ed7654e7d031143173c15abe93?s=32&amp;d=monsterid&amp;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/janweisser\" class=\"reviewer-name\">janweisser</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 30, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">but I wish to be able to edit more details as the site title which is events archive. \nOverall it is a great Plugin and its easy to use.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Straight into my world!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/amazonian1971\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/916bc162aab67a5d46f7d066dfcf82fa?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/916bc162aab67a5d46f7d066dfcf82fa?s=32&amp;d=monsterid&amp;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/amazonian1971\" class=\"reviewer-name\">amazonian1971</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 26, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">\nThis plugin is  kick ass some serious business to do with you know what. It gets you sales. Try it you wont repent...</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Out of this world!</h4>\n	