h this designation, the Groundwork Southcoast Steering Committee received funds and technical assistance from the NPS and EPA to prepare a Feasibility Study and Strategic Plan assessing whether or not Groundwork was appropriate for our community. The strategic plan was approved andan Executive Director was hired in Februaryof 2017.</p>\";s:10:\"margin_top\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"margin_top_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"margin_top_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"margin_bottom\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"margin_bottom_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:24:\"margin_bottom_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"margin_left\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"margin_left_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:22:\"margin_left_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"margin_right\";s:0:\"\";s:19:\"margin_right_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"margin_right_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"responsive_display\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"visibility_display\";s:0:\"\";s:26:\"visibility_user_capability\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"animation\";s:0:\"\";s:15:\"animation_delay\";s:3:\"0.0\";s:2:\"id\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"class\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"rich-text\";s:11:\"connections\";a:1:{s:4:\"text\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:13:\"593457ff7b990\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"node\";s:13:\"593457ff7b990\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"column\";s:6:\"parent\";s:13:\"593329e3e671d\";s:8:\"position\";i:0;s:8:\"settings\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"size\";s:5:\"23.02\";}}s:13:\"593457ff7b794\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"node\";s:13:\"593457ff7b794\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"module\";s:6:\"parent\";s:13:\"593457ff7b990\";s:8:\"position\";i:0;s:8:\"settings\";O:8:\"stdClass\":22:{s:4:\"text\";s:580:\"<div class=\"about-sidebar\">\n\n<a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/who-we-are/mission-statement\">Mission Statement</a>\n\n<a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/who-we-are/why-fall-river-and-new-bedford\">Fall River &amp; New Bedford</a>\n\n<a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/who-we-are/history\">History</a>\n\n<a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/who-we-are/staff