ndwork Trusts. Locally organized and controlled, Groundwork Trusts provide services focused on improving their communities environment, economy, and quality of life.</p>\n<p class=\"large-textbody\">As a Groundwork Trust GWSC represents a strong partnership between government, business, foundations, community groups, and residents. Projects serve a common agenda and are designed to accomplish other goals, such as stewarding urban waterways, brown field reclamation, job training, environmental education, and developing future leaders through targeted youth leadership development. All projects and activities of Groundwork are carried out to leverage resources for residents to transform their own communities.</p>\n\n<h2 class=\"make-green\">What We do</h2>\n\n<hr />\n<p class=\"large-textbody\">GWSC works collaboratively to develop current and future leadership to steward urban waterways and brownfields in environmental justice communities in south eastern Massachusetts.</p>\";s:10:\"margin_top\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"margin_top_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"margin_top_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"margin_bottom\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"margin_bottom_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:24:\"margin_bottom_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"margin_left\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"margin_left_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:22:\"margin_left_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"margin_right\";s:0:\"\";s:19:\"margin_right_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"margin_right_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"responsive_display\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"visibility_display\";s:0:\"\";s:26:\"visibility_user_capability\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"animation\";s:0:\"\";s:15:\"animation_delay\";s:3:\"0.0\";s:2:\"id\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"class\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"rich-text\";s:11:\"connections\";a:1:{s:4:\"text\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:13:\"5934280ee0d14\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"node\";s:13:\"5934280ee0d14\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"column\";s:6:\"parent\";s:13:\"593327b9435f8\";s:8:\"position\";i:0;s:8:\"settings\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"size\";s:5:\"23.02\";}}s:13:\"5934280ee0b76\";O:8:\"stdC