></h3>		\n			<p>Find out about Groundwork SouthCoast and the</p>\n<p>results of all our hard work and great partnerships.</p>\n			<a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/who-we-are/why-fall-river-and-new-bedford\" target=\"_self\" role=\"button\">\n							Learn More\n			</a>\n				<a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/get-involved/volunteer\" target=\"_self\" itemprop=\"url\">\n				<img src=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/12036777_507903089380828_1936469083037503511_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" itemprop=\"image\"  />\n				</a>\n	<h3><a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/get-involved/volunteer\" target=\"_self\"><h3>GET INVOVLED</h3></a></h3>		\n			<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ready to work? Come to one of our many</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">weekend work days and be ready to get dirty.</p>\n			<a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/get-involved/volunteer\" target=\"_self\" role=\"button\">\n							Find Out How\n			</a>\n	','Home Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','4-revision-v1','','','2017-06-04 17:11:57','2017-06-04 17:11:57','',4,'http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/4-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(326,8,'2017-06-04 17:59:17','2017-06-04 17:59:17','\n<h1>Thank you for supporting Groundwork Southcoast!</h1>\n<p>Help support our programming in 2017.</p>\n<p>Your gift to Groundwork Southcoast helps us further our mission to establish and promote environmental equity by increasing access to safe and healthy outdoor spaces, providing local youth with summerjobs, and building a strong successful support for the Southcoast of Massachusetts for years to come.</p>\n<p><em>All donations are tax deductible.</em></p>\n<p><em>Continue to our secure donation page.</em></p>\n			<a href=\"UpdatePaypallLink.com\" target=\"_blank\" role=\"button\">\n						Donate\n					</a>\n<h1>Groundwork Southcoast\'s Wish List</h1>\n<p>Have items laying around? Below is a list of 