ind out about Groundwork SouthCoast and the</p>\n<p>results of all our hard work and great partnerships.</p>\n			<a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/who-we-are/mission-statement\" target=\"_self\" role=\"button\">\n							Learn More\n			</a>\n				<a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/get-involved/volunteer\" target=\"_self\" itemprop=\"url\">\n				<img src=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/12036777_507903089380828_1936469083037503511_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" itemprop=\"image\"  />\n				</a>\n	<h3><a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/get-involved/volunteer\" target=\"_self\"><h3>GET INVOVLED</h3></a></h3>		\n			<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ready to work? Come to one of our many</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">weekend work days and be ready to get dirty.</p>\n			<a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/get-involved/volunteer\" target=\"_self\" role=\"button\">\n							Find Out How\n			</a>\n	','Home Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','4-revision-v1','','','2017-06-04 19:21:48','2017-06-04 19:21:48','',4,'http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/4-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(350,8,'2017-06-04 19:23:08','2017-06-04 19:23:08','\n<p><a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/who-we-are/mission-statement\">Mission Statement</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/who-we-are/why-fall-river-and-new-bedford\">Fall River &amp; New Bedford</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/who-we-are/history\">History</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/who-we-are/staff-and-board\">Staff &amp; Board</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/home-page/what-we-do/our-stories\">Our Stories</a></p>\n	<h1>Why Fall River and New Bedford</h1>\n<hr />\n<p>\nGWSC is the only community-based environmental organization in either city whos organizing focuses on: youth, residents, and other stakeholders in a grassroots-fueled, neighborhood-scale planning and redevelopment initiative aimed at reclaiming vacant, contaminated, underutilized and/or under-maintained land and waterways for community benefit. This whats next? agenda is a strong suit of the Groundwork model and, as such, holds great potential for these two cities as well as building the next generation of organizers and social justice leaders while recognizing the key role that the voice of youth has to play in this work alongside of adult and other marginalized residents.\n</p>\n','Why Fall River and New Bedford','','inherit','closed','closed','','33-revision-v1','','','2017-06-04 19:23:08','2017-06-04 19:23:08','',33,'http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/33-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(351,8,'2017-06-04 19:25:02','2017-06-04 19:25:02','\n				<img src=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/132_3235_0.jpg\" alt=\"132_3235_0\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"400\" width=\"300\"  />\n	<h2 id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1496284038961_223\">FALL RIVER</h2>\nCome help weed with the Friends of the Alfred J. Lima Quequechan River Railroad Trail: Mondays, Wednesdays and Fridays 3:30-4:30pm</p>\n<p>Help talk to your neighbors about Groundwork Southcoast please email: mramsey@groundworksouthcoast.org for more information.</p>\n<h2 id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1496284038961_223\">NEW BEDFORD</h2>\n<p>Help set up or clean up on June 13th for the Love the Ave community meeting. 4:30-8:30pm</p>\n<p>Help talk to your neighbors about Groundwork Southcoast please email: mramsey@groundworksouthcoast.org for more information.\n</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/interest-form\"><button> Let Us Know If You Are Interested!</button></a></p>\n','Volunteer','','inherit','closed','closed','','54-revision-v1','','','2017-06-04 19:25:02','2017-06-04 19:25:02','',54,'http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/54-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(352,8,'2017-06-04 19:27:56','2017-06-04 19:27:56','\n	<h2 id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1496282552477_223\">GREEN TEAM</h2>\n<hr />\n<p>\nThe Groundwork Southcoast<strong></strong>Green Team is a summerprogram that offers part-time, paid positions for up to 12Fall River and New Bedford high school aged students each year to help learn about and lead local environmental and healthy community initiatives, conduct research, raise awareness, and participate in hands-on improvement projects throughout both cities. The program is intended to promote the protection and restoration of the Southcoasts critical ecological systems, natural resources, and public health by engaging teens in advocacy and experiential-learning efforts focused on the community\'s parks, gardens, waterways, and vacant open spaces. The Green Team program has dual goals - to prepare Fall River and New Bedfords youth for a lifetime of environmental and healthy community leadership, and to invest in our communitys future and capacity to improve its physical environment.</p>\n				<img src=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/13315218_1736590056612924_3981364880020552959_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"13315218_1736590056612924_3981364880020552959_n\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"225\" width=\"300\"  />\n				<img src=\"http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/18055969_1898728107065784_7181102866686186357_o-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"18055969_1898728107065784_7181102866686186357_o\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"200\" width=\"300\"  />\n	','Programs','','inherit','closed','closed','','43-revision-v1','','','2017-06-04 19:27:56','2017-06-04 19:27:56','',43,'http://groundworksouth.48in48sites.org/43-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(353,8,'2017-06-04 19:30:50','2017-06-04 19:30:50','\n<h1>Thank you for supporting Groundwork Southcoast!</h1>\n<p>Help support our programming in 2017.</p>\n<p>Your gift to Groundwork Southcoast helps us further our mission to establish and promote environmental equity by increasing access t